{"tid":2165443,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[瑞士] 蘇黎世冇野好睇??","createTime":"2020-08-19T23:20:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T18:21:59.000Z","uid":268265,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fc050b226f80de3992974421ba822a7c7d260816","tid":2165443,"uid":268265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T23:20:55.000Z","msg":"經過一年多, 大家都增加了民主意識, 你哋有人認為蘇黎世冇野睇，好無聊. 其實隨著香港發生的事情, 好值得參觀蘇黎世火車站附近的瑞士國家博物館 (博物館建築都靚, 見下圖)，睇下瑞士的歷史以及為數不多的半直接民主國家之一如何實現其民主。如果會睇埋其他展覽, 半日好易無左. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.landesmuseum.ch/en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.landesmuseum.ch%2Fen&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufRVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=d3baf93a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.landesmuseum.ch/en</a><br />\n<br />\n你睇下人地博物館向老師提供36頁的guiding/teaching material, 係 p.32 (見下表) 大大隻 Topics from Swiss history <span class=\"orange\"><strong>and politics</strong></span>呀! 有人仲話不應該在學校引入政治, 人地瑞士<strong>小學初中</strong>已講 <strong>freedom, morals, civil courage, federalism, women rights</strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNsttOn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNsttOn.png&h=f0f4b452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.landesmuseum.ch/landesmuseum/ihr-besuch/schulen/geschichte-schweiz/190621_ufs_geschichte_ch_lehrerkommentar_englisch.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.landesmuseum.ch%2Flandesmuseum%2Fihr-besuch%2Fschulen%2Fgeschichte-schweiz%2F190621_ufs_geschichte_ch_lehrerkommentar_englisch.pdf&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufRVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=71c66d4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.landesmuseum.ch/landesmuseum/ihr-besuch/schulen/geschichte-schweiz/190621_ufs_geschichte_ch_lehrerkommentar_englisch.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nMore info about the museum:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zuerich.com/en/visit/culture/national-museum-zurich\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zuerich.com%2Fen%2Fvisit%2Fculture%2Fnational-museum-zurich&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufRVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=6e588366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zuerich.com/en/visit/culture/national-museum-zurich</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/styles/gallery_image_l/public/imagegallery/web_zuerich_landesmuseum_luftaufnahme_2.jpg?itok=MLX3kCTX&amp;timestamp=1494587390\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.zuerich.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fgallery_image_l%2Fpublic%2Fimagegallery%2Fweb_zuerich_landesmuseum_luftaufnahme_2.jpg%3Fitok%3DMLX3kCTX%26timestamp%3D1494587390&h=7fd0a7a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/crowdriff-media/mirror/aa3c52ca8b150d46104bcd1fc8612e94870202ce948b276bd0500e1db52ec078.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.amazonaws.com%2Fcrowdriff-media%2Fmirror%2Faa3c52ca8b150d46104bcd1fc8612e94870202ce948b276bd0500e1db52ec078.jpg&h=fc211a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘇黎世同附近其實仲有其他好野玩, 不過大家可能覺去得瑞士都係睇山雪好主.  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=我去過,正 /  有興趣! <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=我去過,悶死 /  no thanks!"},{"pid":"2b63699fba292d38069c46e9e5da4bad37aa92de","tid":2165443,"uid":283494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T23:47:04.000Z","msg":"去蘇黎世，最值得睇係睇顧客，珠寶店之顧客。市中心成條街珠寶店，顧客非富則貴，高官，將軍，大使，法官，富商，毒梟，情婦，二世祖，應有盡有，而且係國際級。<br />\n<br />\n見過有豪客包場買珠寶。行完珠寶店，立即覺得自己窮到死。"},{"pid":"2074926850c2c8b5d9f45b1eaf7c1bc29c5d6453","tid":2165443,"uid":60129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T23:51:33.000Z","msg":"蘇黎世好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能唔係有錢人<br />\n<br />\n早之放多啲係山區/去日內瓦"},{"pid":"e0987ca9bd5b851ff635