. 包場嗰過又唔係我, 唔會行珠寶店, 未行已覺得自己窮到死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1782a00a858043d165df1064cb8f835bbdfc19f","tid":2165443,"uid":268265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2074926850c2c8b5d9f45b1eaf7c1bc29c5d6453","tid":2165443,"uid":60129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T23:51:33.000Z","msg":"蘇黎世好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能唔係有錢人<br />\n<br />\n早之放多啲係山區/去日內瓦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"日內瓦都唔平喎同好似冇乜野玩? <br />\n<br />\n咁我又冇話蘇黎世好玩過瑞士其他地方, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過見大家咁嫌棄蘇黎世, 大家又爭取民主普選成年, 幫佢出下聲, 主要推下佢個國家博物館 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係有錢人: 國家博物館CHF10 睇半日. (Zurich Card 包埋 )  <a href=\"https://www.zuerich.com/en/visit/your-city-travel-pass?gclid=EAIaIQobChMIy_WYw6Wp6wIVk9wYCh25eQOVEAAYASAAEgJHJfD_BwE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zuerich.com%2Fen%2Fvisit%2Fyour-city-travel-pass%3Fgclid%3DEAIaIQobChMIy_WYw6Wp6wIVk9wYCh25eQOVEAAYASAAEgJHJfD_BwE&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufRVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=2a5ec935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zuerich.com/en/visit/your-city-travel-pass?gclid=EAIaIQobChMIy_WYw6Wp6wIVk9wYCh25eQOVEAAYASAAEgJHJfD_BwE</a> <br />\n唔使license 租1粒鐘 motor boat CHF70 (最多四人) <br />\n湖邊12連環船 wine tasting  CHF27 (全日)<br />\n不過當然唔係人人鐘意.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我明風景係有睇頭啲 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vWpvLvV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvWpvLvV.jpg&h=9541c376&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a10ff17b70b0ec7eee1130ea638f07214e63115","tid":2165443,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:39:01.000Z","msg":"香港跟本要瑞士化. 做中立國. 乜柒都要公投."},{"pid":"7dc63da86059f17e585fd03903b72e4d65014705","tid":2165443,"uid":288511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:57:21.000Z","msg":"博物館有個展館介紹瑞士嘅名作家<br />\n包括社會契約論Jean-Jacques Rousseau <br />\n人道主義先驅Henry Dunant <br />\n新教加爾文主義Jean Calvin<br />\n講解佢哋點樣塑造當代瑞士社會<br />\n好值得一睇"},{"pid":"a995a68f61b76b940daba3954f0250026fdca46e","tid":2165443,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"262268251aba281b5d55c0f11c7a4af520739688","tid":2165443,"uid":268265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b63699fba292d38069c46e9e5da4bad37aa92de","tid":2165443,"uid":283494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T23:47:04.000Z","msg":"去蘇黎世，最值得睇係睇顧客，珠寶店之顧客。市中心成條街珠寶店，顧客非富則貴，高官，將軍，大使，法官，富商，毒梟，情婦，二世祖，應有盡有，而且係國際級。<br />\n<br />\n見過有豪客包場買珠寶。行完珠寶店，立即覺得自己窮到死。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:28:30.000Z","msg":"巴打你認真?<br />\n<br />\n<em>最值得睇係睇顧客</em>  <br />\n好睇在? <br />\n<br />\n<em>見過有豪客包場買珠寶。</em> <br />\n包場買珠寶名牌常有. 包場嗰過又唔係我, 唔會行珠寶店, 未行已覺得自己窮到死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:58:39.000Z","msg":"去旅行，增廣見聞，睇一d 香港冇嘅嘢。蘇黎世Bahnhofstrasse 街上行人，富貴比率高到離奇，睇佢地d打扮，保鏢，排場，行路姿勢，選擇貨式，大開眼界。"},{"pid":"3595d2546b2f4425b2a116566dccb6177c7c6a4b","tid":2165443,"uid":268265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a10ff17b70b0ec7eee1130ea638f07214e63115","tid":2165443,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:39:01.000Z","msg":"香港跟本要瑞士化. 做中立國. 乜柒都要公投."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:09:56.000Z","msg":"有好有唔好, 好嬲佢中立唔幫香港 (其實都係幫瑞士自己) , 同有啲野係要時間, 你睇下上面瑞士小學初中已教啲乜? <br />\n<br />\n個貼純見到大家講到好想香港有自由民主, 啲人話瑞士點好點好,  咁去到瑞士旅行睇景外,都可以去人地國家博物館,了解下人地點解可以 run 到半直接民主. <br />\n<br />\n____<br />\n相係瑞士, 但唔係蘇黎世, 純放多少少相等大家冇咁悶. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/niU7Phk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FniU7Phk.jpg&h=ed39d45d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f03a868699e2a93a7fb59cbf4b6b58787f6b6127","tid":2165443,"uid":268265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dc63da86059f17